{"id": 966, "genre": 1001, "title": "你如何理解“对自己好一点”？", "description": "现在谁都让你“对自己好一点”，那你觉得啥叫“对自己好一点”？（题图来自：HELENA PEREZ GARCIA）", "record_count": 4659, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130037SnALpkM5UeTPlHWu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-01T01:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 72448, "content": "别被负面情绪绑架", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591523}, {"id": 72704, "content": "不要为了别人对自己不好伤心难过…别人给不了的自己给足", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453683}, {"id": 73216, "content": "就是对只愿意和自己暧昧的对象付出一些了，多了，就有这想法了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 555123}, {"id": 74240, "content": "有底气才不会委屈到自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593834}, {"id": 72449, "content": "就是要对自己狠一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562328}, {"id": 72705, "content": "对自己负责", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 537979}, {"id": 72961, "content": "我觉得是尽量做到不要委屈自己，同时不要做自己讨厌的那种人", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592329}, {"id": 72706, "content": " 少说点“这怨我”、“对不起”、“我来吧”…", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581425}, {"id": 72962, "content": "不要让负面情绪影响到自己～", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592335}, {"id": 73218, "content": "自己快乐就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592980}, {"id": 72451, "content": "别为了自己的快乐感到有罪", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562900}, {"id": 72707, "content": "对自己狠一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334297}, {"id": 72963, "content": "自己快乐舒坦，咱们就怎么着", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590494}, {"id": 73219, "content": "不要太选择生气。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487957}, {"id": 72452, "content": "自己最好的时候遇见那个她", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591543}, {"id": 72708, "content": "幸福就是能实现你心中的想法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592013}, {"id": 72453, "content": "想玩游戏就玩想看动漫就看", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590742}, {"id": 72709, "content": "吃想吃的，买想买的。但不是放纵也不是奢侈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562336}, {"id": 72454, "content": "不熟的人给你发结婚请帖，委婉但坚决地推辞", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68429}, {"id": 72710, "content": "睡到自然醒", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 375024}, {"id": 72966, "content": "顺心意，事情来了自然身随心动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 377446}, {"id": 73222, "content": "快乐，在做不喜欢事情的基础上还能常做喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592981}, {"id": 73478, "content": "今天乘坐顺风车凯迪拉克，以后也开这么好的车咋样", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589861}, {"id": 81926, "content": "学会享受 学会拒绝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622537}, {"id": 72711, "content": "做想做的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579512}, {"id": 72967, "content": "无忧无虑吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592338}, {"id": 72456, "content": "别爱太满，别睡太晚。多喝水，多运动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573075}, {"id": 72712, "content": "买买买", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157195}, {"id": 72968, "content": "倾听自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590213}, {"id": 72713, "content": "想谁就去见，想吃的就吃，喜欢一件衣服就买，生活就该这样", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586102}, {"id": 72458, "content": "花更多的时间取悦自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591566}, {"id": 72714, "content": "不逾矩，内心严厉，外在待人宽厚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 538522}, {"id": 72970, "content": "不再给自己树立围栏，多给自己一些自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592339}, {"id": 72715, "content": "别委屈了自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469945}, {"id": 72716, "content": "躺猪24个小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536826}, {"id": 72972, "content": "要做点什么都不被圈子束缚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566215}, {"id": 72461, "content": "在特定不能改变事实的时候，尽量顺从自己的内心。不为金钱所劳役", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193521XPcvuRIe1xhdpBiS.jpg", "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591575}, {"id": 72717, "content": "别让我承担的太多 我想承担适合我这个年纪该承担的", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485495}, {"id": 72973, "content": "不为他人改变自己事先的安排", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 570809}, {"id": 72718, "content": "失落时，好好努力，不颓废！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207748}, {"id": 72974, "content": "有稳定的性生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592343}, {"id": 73998, "content": "有些事情，是需要取舍，然而我们的抉择确往往事与愿违", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595206}, {"id": 75278, "content": "懂得拒绝别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600246}, {"id": 72463, "content": "不减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450194}, {"id": 73231, "content": "主要是对自己心情或是心态", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566742}, {"id": 73743, "content": "哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594496}, {"id": 72720, "content": "就是我可以吃吃喝喝玩耍了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592014}, {"id": 72976, "content": "心境平和", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 483588}, {"id": 74512, "content": "想买的东西都有能力满足自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595067}, {"id": 72465, "content": "分手了就拉黑 再也不联系", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493631}]}